author: COMSOL
description: This example models the process of ice sublimation in a vial under vacuum-chamber conditions, a test case for many freeze-drying setups. The example uses the Deformed Geometry interface to compute the coupled heat and mass balances to handle the advancing vapor-ice interface through porous medium.
